{"tid":1115234,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好鍾意係街淫叫","createTime":"2019-04-19T04:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T04:49:56.000Z","uid":61543,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75f18db292aef24dd56791b53aa35cd6de6c05f1","tid":1115234,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:49:56.000Z","msg":"今年20歲 <br />\n淫底 佢日日係街淫叫<br />\n係突然叫嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初頭佢咁樣搞到大家好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但耐咗之後 搞到啲fd都叫埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我地成班出街個個都會係度無啦啦叫<br />\n我地覺得咁樣可以抒發内心想扑野 想食仔嘅欲望 係野性嘅叫囂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋可以吸引啲仔留意我地班基佬<br />\n最勁嗰個朋友試過有幾次叫到同幾條陌生男人扑埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}